snippet.title: Everleigh Rose
snippet.description:
Hi guys! I'm Everleigh Rose and I'm 4 years old. My mommy and daddy are Cole & Sav.. you may know them from their youtube channel! I LOVE TOYS.. but who doesn't?! I also really love to dance and dance on a competition team! Singing is another hobby of mine & I really really love playing with my baby dolls. 

I love making videos and I can't wait to keep posting! I'll be posting every tuesday so make sure you subscribe to my channel! I hope you guys love my videos! Make sure to follow me on Instagram where I post pictures- @EverleighRose! 

Also make sure you subscribe to my family channel, link below!
